rows.label: tlk41310141_04_msg0001
rows.name:
The reason I'm alive today is
thanks to Vandham-san.

rows.label: tlk41310141_04_msg0002
rows.name:
If it were Vandham-san, I don't think
he would have just left the immigrants to fend
for themselves.

rows.label: tlk41310141_04_msg0003
rows.name:
That's why I've decided to accept the immigrants.
Though I'd rather not get involved with people
from Superbia.
